data.description: **Save Hundreds per month with a low 3% Assumable FHA mortgage Loan on the remaining primary loan amount - contact agent for details!** Welcome Home to this functional and open bungalow home in Commerce City. You'll Be Greeted with An Abundance of Light and a Functional Floor Plan that opens into the Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Countertops, and smooth top Range. Beyond the large family room you will find 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Current back room is being used as a bedroom but would function perfectly as a large bonus room or additional family room! Relax In the Backyard under the large patio cover which is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy low energy bills with the Photovoltaic Solar Panels! Fantastic street appeal with new front yard landscaping and fence as well as new oversized concrete driveway to the attached garage! Amazing location as your 6 minutes from Central park, where a moderate walk can get you to Dicks Sporting Goods Park for sports and concerts and Paradice Island Pool and Park is .7 miles away for the warm summer days. You will have a huge selection of tremendous local restaurants nearby. Easy access to Highway 270 and I70. Call now to book your showing!
